        <obo:IAO_0000115>A relation between a microbe and a growth medium indicating that the microbe has been demonstrated to grow in that medium under some set of conditions. This relation represents a generalization from experimental observations reported in the literature or databases; it does not imply that the microbe will grow in the medium under all conditions.</obo:IAO_0000115>
