        <obo:IAO_0000115>A quality that categorizes biological agents according to their hazard level and required containment measures.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <oboInOwl:hasRelatedSynonym>Safety information.risk assessment.biosafety level</oboInOwl:hasRelatedSynonym>
