        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/metpo/1000186"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>A material entity that provides the nutrients and environmental conditions necessary for the cultivation of microorganisms in vitro. Growth media may be liquid (broth) or solid (agar-based) and are formulated to support the growth of specific types of organisms.</obo:IAO_0000115>
