        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/metpo/1007080"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>Test-outcome phenotype where the catalase test yields a positive result (visible bubbling on H2O2). The underlying enzyme-organism relation should additionally be asserted via &lt;organism&gt; METPO:2000302 &apos;shows activity of&apos; GO:0004096 &apos;catalase activity&apos;.</obo:IAO_0000115>
