        <obo:IAO_0000115>Test-outcome phenotype where the coagulase test yields a positive result (plasma clotting). The underlying enzyme-organism relation should additionally be asserted via &lt;organism&gt; METPO:2000302 &apos;shows activity of&apos; &lt;coagulase enzyme term&gt; once a sufficiently specific enzyme term is selected (no GO/EC term currently exists at the bacteriological coagulase test granularity).</obo:IAO_0000115>
